Coco -- True C coroutines for Lua
---------------------------------

Coco is a small extension to get True C Coroutine semantics for Lua 5.1.

Homepage: http://coco.luajit.org/

Coco is Copyright (C) 2005-2009 Mike Pall.
Coco is free software, released under the MIT/X license.

---------------------------------

Full documentation for Coco is available in HTML format.
Please point your favourite browser to:

 doc/index.html

Detailed installation instructions are here:

 doc/install.html

